org.greatage.ioc.scope
Class AbstractScope

java.lang.Object
  org.greatage.ioc.scope.AbstractScope
All Implemented Interfaces:
Scope
Direct Known Subclasses:
GlobalScope, ThreadScope
public abstract class AbstractScope
extends java.lang.Object
implements Scope

This class represents abstract Scope implementation that look ups service instance inside the scope and if it is not found creates new instance using specified service builder.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Ivan Khalopik
